  <title>
    <phrase>Close all</phrase>
  </title>
  <para>
    This command closes all images you have opened. The main
    window remaining empty is that corresponding to the last
    opened image.
  </para>

  <sect3>
    <title>
      <phrase>Activate the Command</phrase>
    </title>
    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          You can access this command from the image menubar through
          <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Close All</guimenuitem></menuchoice>,
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          or by using the keyboard shortcut
          <keycombo><keycap>Shift</keycap><keycap>Ctrl</keycap><keycap>W</keycap></keycombo>.
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </sect3>
</sect2>
